<br>
I autojoin the scarab channel so I can keep up with what is going on and maybe join a group if one is forming or needing more people. I like reading what people are doing and normal conversation etc. <br>
<br>
Last night Chai started using the channel to try and sell some stuff. I put up a note to the channel asking whether this was the correct use for the channel, no response. Well Chai continued so I eventually left the channel. He wasn't spamming or anything, just the occasional post. If I want to see what is for sale etc I can join the bazaar channel and do it there, that is what that channel is for.<br>
<br>
My worry is that if more people start using the channel for selling then I and others will leave the channel and miss out on groups and stuff. My request is that we do not use the channel for selling.<br>
<br>
Your thoughts please. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=186665">Thug - 60 War</A>
